it.csi.mddtools.guigen

Interface ActivateMultiPanelItemCommand

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Command, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier

    public interface ActivateMultiPanelItemCommand
extends Command
    A representation of the model object 'Activate Multi Panel Item Command'. Permette di visualizzare uno degli item di un MultiPanel (o di una delle sue sottoclassi TabSetPanel o WizardPanel).

    The following features are supported:

    • Multipanel
    • Active Item
    See Also:
    GuigenPackage.getActivateMultiPanelItemCommand()
